comments: Allen (BKN) establishes a legal position in Ferguson's (OKC) path and does not deliver contact.
Ferguson (OKC) moves into LeVert's (BKN) body and initiates contact that affects his driving shot attempt.
Allen (BKN) and Adams (OKC) briefly engage and separate during the rebound.
Harris (BKN) maintains a legal guarding position during the driving shot by Schroder (OKC).
Allen (BKN) establishes a legal position in Schroder's (OKC) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Adams (OKC) makes marginal contact with Dinwiddie (BKN) during the driving shot attempt however, Dinwiddie (BKN) is able to move through the contact and finish at the rim.
Adams (OKC) establishes a legal position in LeVert's (BKN) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) maintains a legal guarding position during LeVert's (BKN) drive to the basket.
Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) cleanly dislodges the ball from Allen (BKN).
Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) maintains a legal guarding position during LeVert's (BKN) shot attempt.
Adams (OKC) establishes a legal position in LeVert's (BKN) path and does not deliver contact.
Allen (BKN) maintains legal position as Paul (OKC) loses control of the ball during his drive.
Schroder (OKC) dislodges Allen (BKN) from his position during the inbound.
Adams (OKC) makes incidental contact to the arm of Dinwiddie (BKN) after the release that does not affect his driving shot attempt.
